	<li class="reprints ca-5"><a href="https://s100.copyright.com/AppDispatchServlet?publisherName=TIME&amp;publication=TIME&amp;title=Kim+Jong+Il+Dies%3A+North+Korea+Looks+to+His+Son+Kim+Jong+Un++%2D+TIME&amp;publicationDate=12/19/2011&amp;author=&amp;contentID=2102781&amp;orderBeanReset=true" title="Reprints &amp; Permissions" target="_blank"><span class="icon"></span>Reprints</a></li>
